CIESIN</Author><Publication_Date>1996-12-31T00:00:00.000Z</Publication_Date><Title>Archive of Census Related Products (ACRP): 1990 Street Intersections</Title><Edition>1.00</Edition><Publication_Place>Saginaw, MI</Publication_Place><Publisher>NASA Socioeconomic Data and Applications Center (SEDAC)</Publisher><Persistent_Identifier><Type>DOI</Type><Identifier>10.7927/H42Z13FP</Identifier></Persistent_Identifier></Reference><Summary><Abstract>The 1990 Census Block Statistics portion of the Archive of Census Related Products (ACRP) contains population and housing data from the U.S. Census Bureau's 1990 Summary Tape File (STF1B). The population data includes total population, age, race, and hispanic origin, while the housing data comprises number of housing Units, tenure, room density, mean contract rent, mean value, and mean number of rooms. Additional data includes land area, water area, centroids, Metropolitan Statistical Area (MSA) codes, place codes, and special area codes.  This portion of the ACRP is produced by the Columbia University Center for International Earth Science Information Network (CIESIN).</Abstract><Purpose>To provide population and housing data for the U.S.</Purpose></Summary><Related_URL><URL_Content_Type><Type>GET RELATED VISUALIZATION</Type></URL_Content_Type><URL>https://sedac.ciesin.columbia.edu/downloads/maps/acrp/acrp-census-block-stats-1990/sedac-logo.jpg</URL><Description>Sample browse graphic of the data set.</Description></Related_URL><Related_URL><URL_Content_Type><Type>GET DATA</Type><Subtype>DIRECT DOWNLOAD</Subtype></URL_Content_Type><URL>https://sedac.ciesin.columbia.edu/data/set/acrp-census-block-stats-1990/data-download</URL><Description>Data Download Page</Description></Related_URL><Related_URL><URL_Content_Type><Type>VIEW RELATED INFORMATION</Type><Subtype>GENERAL DOCUMENTATION</Subtype></URL_Content_Type><URL>https://sedac.ciesin.columbia.edu/data/set/acrp-census-block-stats-1990</URL><Description>Data SetÂ Overview Page</Description></Related_URL><IDN_Node><Short_Name>CIESIN_SEDAC_ACRP_1990_CBS</Short_Name></IDN_Node><Metadata_Name>CEOS IDN DIF</Metadata_Name><Metadata_Version>VERSION 10.2</Metadata_Version><Metadata_Dates><Metadata_Creation>1996-01-01</Metadata_Creation><Metadata_Last_Revision>2021-05-19</Metadata_Last_Revision><Data_Creation>1996-12-31T00:00:00.000Z</Data_Creation><Data_Last_Revision>1996-12-31T00:00:00.000Z</Data_Last_Revision></Metadata_Dates><Product_Level_Id>2</Product_Level_Id><Collection_Data_Type>SCIENCE_QUALITY</Collection_Data_Type></DIF>
